{SOUTH has 5 points, so she responds 2\D to NORTH's opening 2\C bid.

NORTH bids his 5-card \S suit.

SOUTH is too good for the second negative, so she supports NORTH's \S.

NORTH doesn't have enough to think about slam, so he signs off at 4\S.}

