[Student "S"]
{SOUTH opens 2\C and NORTH, with 8 points should bid 2\H. 

SOUTH should bid his \S suit at his second turn.

And NORTH can only rebid the 6-card \Hs.

That's enough for SOUTH to hear. He bids 6\H, or, just as 
good, he might bid 6NT.}

